      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLDEN SUNSET (6) put the writing on the wall with a much better showing last week, coming from the back row for a 2.5m second top topliner Gus. That was her third outing off a let-up so she should be peaking now and owns a strong strike rate at this circuit and distance. AJAY VOLSTEAD (8) has some ground to make up on GOLDEN SUNSET through last week's fifth but he beat her when scoring in January, part of a string of wins and placings he put together at this circuit. Draws for a trail and could be dangerous. ZEALOUS SPUR NZ (7) is player off a better effort for third from the back row last week. ALDEBARANSTILINSKI (3) goes up in grade but draws well and is hard to knock off a hat trick of wins here.",
